The paper proposes a method for causal relationship exploration in data using decision trees. This falls under the domain of machine learning and data science, which are covered by several arXiv CS sub-categories. Specifically, cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) are the most likely categories as they cover topics related to decision trees and causal inference. Additionally, cs.ST (Statistics) and cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) are also possible categories as they cover statistical methods and their applications in various fields, including data analytics.
